description_text:
These data points can be used in the VIS editor for color settings.

For instance '0', enter the desired data point including the curly brackets. (If you have chosen a different instance number, replace the 0 with your number.)

Examples for colors:
{vis-inventwo.0.CSS.Button}
{vis-inventwo.0.CSS.Active}
{vis-inventwo.0.CSS.Text}

For striped areas, the following code can be entered in the color field:
repeating-linear-gradient(-45deg, #333333 0px, #333333 15px, #393939 15px, #393939 30px, #333333 30px)
